| # | Criterion | Verification |
|---|-----------|--------------|
| 1.1 | Contains project summary with all six canonical states | Grep for `IDLE`, `EVAL`, `SELECT`, `EXEC`, `POST`, `HARDSTOP` |
| 1.2 | Quick-start section with clone, verify, regenerate commands | Run commands in a fresh clone |
| 1.3 | Architecture overview with text diagram | Visual inspection |
| 1.4 | Canonical state name table (9 entries) | Count rows: 6 states + LSPS + HardstopRecoverThm + HardstopToIdle |
| 1.5 | Figures section with alt text + captions for all 3 figures | Each figure has ≥2-sentence alt text and a caption |
| 1.6 | Reproduction steps with prerequisites | Steps produce identical output when run |
