## Deliverable 3: Figure Set (`paper/figures/fig[1-3]_*`)

| # | Criterion | Verification |
|---|-----------|--------------|
| 3.1 | Three figures, each in SVG + PDF (6 files total) | `ls paper/figures/fig*.{svg,pdf}` returns 6 files |
| 3.2 | fig1: Shows 5-state ring + HARDSTOP spur + HardstopToIdle arc | Visual: ring of 5 + box below + green arrow back |
| 3.3 | fig2: Shows 4-stage LSPS pipeline with feedback loop | Visual: Latch→Select→Post→Switch + return arc |
